review: Excellent experience. Madam was quite gentle and humble in listening to our problems and then explained the issue in such a way that even a layman can understand. In fact I haven't  seen such a doctor in my life who takes such keen interest in their patients wellbeing and advises the patient all the pros and cons of the treatment. I request all the so called patients to visit madam for their OBG problems personally and you will see a miracle in your life. Thank you madam for your wonderful advice.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I have visited Dr Padmalatha for difficulties in conceiving, I am extremely happy with the treatment given by her. I had conceived within 6 months of meeting her. It took 6 months because she has started medicine after tried all natural possible options. Her patience level to listen us and explanation of each and every detail is wonderful.
She has supported in all way even during the corona time. I have delivered 15 days before with c section. As there were no family members with us due to covid situation, the way Dr Padmalatha has supported both medically and emotionally during and after delivery is overwhelming for me and my husband.
Even the staff was very cooperative and friendly.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Dr. Padmalatha is very caring and friendly. She gives a huge mental support and just free us from all our worries and tensions. She educates patients to avoid the disease and eliminates the problems by attacking on root cause. She prescribes for only those tests which are relevant to the patient and avoid such treatment which has its side effects. She always treat patient like her own family member and advice the best treatment which cures the disease and heals the patient rapidly. She also gives awareness on several diseases, and precautionary methods to avoid. She explains very nicely the functions of the organs and pros and cons of dysfunction. During emergencies, she supports on calls and advice promptly. *** ** *** ** *** **** ************* * *** ** **********

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Pregnancy,Pregnant,Pregnancy Check Up,Pregnancy care and management,
review: Hi,As soon as I got pregnant we were in search of doctor. we checked in practo for gynecologist and finalized Dr. Padmalatha after considering the reviews in practo and distance from home to sparsh hospital. we were in contact with doctor throughout my pregnancy and delivery. I was diagnosed with covid during my 8 weeks pregnancy and she helped us in being positive during this time and suggested blood tests and gave confidence that it won't affect the baby growth. She was understanding the covid situation outside and in hospital and was not asking us to visit frequently for unnecessary reasons. only if it's required and in case of emergency only she told us to visit hospital. She insisted in right scan and tablets during my journey. I was having fibroids in uterus and doctor gave clear explanation about it. On any questions we had doctor would give us clear explanation and clarity on the same. Doctor was confident about normal delivery for me. During my delivery time she came on the right time and delivered baby safe. we are very Thankful to doctor for safe pregnancy and delivery. Doctor gave all confidence and my journey of delivery was smooth without any problem. I would definitely refer this doctor to have safe and happy pregnancy and delivery. the confidence the doctor gives and support during the journey will be helpful for any person. she clarifies with happy face. and would answer all our questions even asked multiple times. Thanks Dr. Padmalatha,Kavya Madhusudhan.

review:
Doctor Padmalatha is a gem of a person. As we went to hospital without appointment, we had to wait for almost 5 hours. But the wait was worth it. 

Doctor went through all our medical history and explained us what are the options available for treatment and suggested us the right one.

My mother was a cardiac patient and had to undergo vaginal hysterectomy. Giving her a right Anastasia was the task here, because after Anastasia the heart may behave differently since my mother was a cardiac patient. We somehow with the help of anaesthetist concluded the Anastasia that‚Äôs right for my Amma.

Then the surgery was performed by the doctor and it was done normally through vaginal without any C section. It was the doctors effort and my mother‚Äôs cooperation that made the surgery simple and mother recovered very soon. 

Not only that regular check ups were done to ensure there is no problem and health is good.

tags: Treatment satisfaction,Explanation of the health issue,Doctor friendliness,
review:
I was admitted to the emergency for lower abdominal pain,after a prolonged diagnosis by the medical team,  I was diagnosed by ectopic pregnancy ( already at life threatening stage) which I was unaware I was suffering from past 3 days. Dr Padmalatha after diagnosis gave immediate medical care by laparoscopic surgery and saved my life.
The post surgery healing is also been happening well due to proper medication. 
I would really like to thank Dr Padmalatha for her exact diagnosis and treatment in time which could save my life ..!!
